dcterms:description: The PartNet dataset consists of 573,585 fine-grained part annotations for 26,671 shapes across 24 different 3D object categories. Most of the 3D objects are annotated at three levels: coarse, middle, and fine-grained levels.
dcterms:title: PartNet
